Subject: Kingston USB
Description:
A user has been given a Kingston USB stick and EasyLock has been installed on it by somebody else. He has been given the password for it but when he clicks EasyLock application gets message "The EndPoint Protector Client is missing. EasyLock will now close." 
Does not get the chance to put the password in. 
Looks like something needs to be installed. 
Are you able to help with this ?
